OL,5, Convicted criminals could be forced to 
OL,6, appear in court for sentencing, the    
OL,7, justice secretary has told Zara        
OL,8, Aleena's family.                       
OL,10,FDominic Raab is examining whether      
OL,11,Fjudges should be able to impose longer 
OL,12,Fterms on those who refuse to appear.   
OL,14,FMs Aleena's killer Jordan McSweeney    
OL,15,Frefused to attend his sentencing,      
OL,16,Fsomething her family described as "a   
OL,17,Fslap in the face".                     
OL,19,FMr Raab told the BBC convicts attending
OL,20,Fwas the "least the victims deserve".   
